Message.message: Watch out! If that monster sees you, you're a goner for sure!
Make sure not to step on those sharp spikes either!
I can't hit the switch with my hand, because... uh.... that just wouldn't look nearly as cool!
Bullseye!
I'd better watch out, those look like some really sharp spikes, and definitely not just like four squares on the ground
This dungeon sure is dangerous... but it will all pay off!
I've heard a legend that if I get to the end of this dungeon and defeat the ultimate monster, there'll be a huge treasure!
And there better not be some "The treasure was me the whole time" twist...
Uh oh. Speaking of monsters, there's one now. It'll probably chase after me if it sees me.
I've gotta make sure to kill all the monsters, so they won't fight me on my way out
Hah! Killed two monsters with one stone!
I don't care how tough you think you are "ultimate monster", I'm coming for you!
Press action to fire an arrow! How do you like a piece of that!
I think if I fire an arrow, I might be able to hit that switch
"Why are you killing us off!?"
"I have a family!"
Oh...
Oh god...
The treasure wasn't me the whole time...
The ultimate monster was...
I've gotta make sure to kill all the monsters
